      <abstract label="Abstract:">Research collection of photographic slides, publications,
        and notes on Ragamala painting.</abstract>
      <langmaterial label="Language:">Collection material in <language encodinganalog="041" langcode="eng">English</language></langmaterial>
    </did>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
      <p>Research collection of photographic slides, publications, and notes on Ragamala
        painting. Materials were gathered while Ebeling was conducting research for his book
        Ragamala Painting, published in 1973.</p>
    </scopecontent>
